CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.3
-------------------------

    o A bug in the test code was fixed (exposed by new 'testthat').
      This version does not change behavior of the apeglm functions.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.2
-------------------------

    o A bug in the calculation of the prior is fixed. This was
      identified by Cecile Le Sueur.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.1
-------------------------

    o A parameter 'multiplier' was elevated to an argument in apeglm(),
      and the default value changed.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
-------------------------

    o apeglm is released on Bioconductor! Methods can be accessed
      from within DESeq2 by calling 'lfcShrink' with type="apeglm".
